#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:496
msgid "Custom domain normalization"
msgstr "自定义域名归一化"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:498
msgid "1. Rules affect domain filtering logic, reflected in the sidebar \"Domains\" module and favicon-based domain filtering.<br> 2. Each line configures one rule. There are two types of rules:<br> (1) Subdomain normalization: e.g., <code>a.com</code> normalizes <code>1.a.com</code> and <code>2.a.com</code> under <code>a.com</code><br> (2) Cross-domain mapping: e.g., <code>b.com -> a.com</code> normalizes <code>1.b.com</code> and <code>2.b.com</code> under <code>a.com</code><br> 3. After configuring a subdomain normalization rule like <code>a.com</code>, adding a subdomain like <code>3.a.com</code> keeps <code>3.a.com</code> unnormalized:<br> (1) In the sidebar \"Domains\" module, <code>a.com</code> expands to show <code>3.a.com</code> separately<br> (2) Clicking the favicon of <code>3.a.com</code> bookmarks will not force filtering by <code>a.com</code><br> 4. After configuring a cross-domain mapping rule like <code>b.com -> a.com</code>, adding a rule like <code>b.com</code> keeps <code>b.com</code> unnormalized:<br> (1) In the sidebar \"Domains\" module, <code>a.com</code> expands to show <code>b.com</code> separately<br> (2) Clicking the favicon of <code>b.com</code> bookmarks will not force filtering by <code>a.com</code>"
msgstr "1. 规则会影响域名筛选逻辑。体现在侧边栏「域名」功能模块，和点击书签 favicon 进行的域名筛选。<br>2. 每行配置一条规则，有如下两种类型规则：<br>(1) 子域名归一化：如 <code>a.com</code>，那么 <code>1.a.com</code>、<code>2.a.com</code> 都会归一化到 <code>a.com</code><br>(2) 跨域名映射：如 <code>b.com -> a.com</code>，那么 <code>1.b.com</code>、<code>2.b.com</code> 都会归一化到 <code>a.com</code><br>3. 配置一条子域名归一化规则后如 <code>a.com</code>，再配置一条其子域名如 <code>3.a.com</code>，可以使得 <code>3.a.com</code> 不被归一化，这是指<br>(1) 在侧边栏「域名」模块中，<code>a.com</code> 可展开，其下会单独展示 <code>3.a.com</code><br>(2) 点击 <code>3.a.com</code> 相关书签的 favicon，不会被强制按 <code>a.com</code> 筛选<br>4. 配置一条跨域名映射规则后如 <code>b.com -> a.com</code>，再配置一条其域名规则如 <code>b.com</code>，可以使得 <code>b.com</code> 不被归一化，这是指<br>(1) 在侧边栏「域名」模块中，<code>a.com</code> 可展开，其下会单独展示 <code>b.com</code><br>(2) 点击 <code>b.com</code> 相关书签的 favicon，不会被强制按 <code>a.com</code> 筛选"

